              ],
              "free_text": [
                " Half-life of 4.174+-0.004 sec was obtained from",
                "analysis of N-17 decay curve.",
                "Level energies, neutron widths of neutron emitting",
                "states in O-17 (Table 2 of NP/A,274,45,1976),",
                "intensities of neutron branch from O-17 levels",
                " (Abstract of NP/A,274,45,1976)",
                "Elvl,keV         Intensity, %       Width, keV",
                "4549.3+-1.3      34.8+-2.6          54.8+-0.4",
                "5081.+-21.       0.6+-0.4           113.+-55.",
                "5387.1+-1.2      52.7+-3.5          63.2+-1.1",
                "5949.9+-1.9      7.0+-0.5           60.5+-3.2",
                "Absolute intensities normalized to Pn=(95+-1)% from",
                "J.Tomlinson, At.Data and Nucl.Data Tables,12,179,1973.",
                " Table 3 - Absolute intensities and log ft values.",
                " Table 4 - Exp. asymmetry in mirror decays of the",
                "mass-17 system."
              ]
            }
          ],
